#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:1
msgid "Qwen3.5-397B-A17B Deployment Tutorial"
msgstr "Qwen3.5-397B-A17B 部署教程"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:3
msgid "1 Introduction"
msgstr "1.简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:5
msgid ""
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B is a large-scale Qwen3.5 MoE model that combines "
"multimodal capability, long-context inference, MTP speculative decoding, and"
" W8A8 quantized deployment for production serving on Ascend hardware."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B 是一个大规模 Qwen3.5 MoE 模型，融合了多模态能力、长上下文推理、MTP 推测解码和 W8A8 "
"量化部署，可在 Ascend 硬件上用于生产服务。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:7
msgid ""
"This document describes the main validation steps for the model, including "
"supported features, prerequisites, installation, single-node online "
"deployment, multi-node deployment, Prefill-Decode (PD) disaggregation, "
"functional verification, accuracy and performance evaluation, performance "
"tuning, and FAQs."
msgstr ""
"本文档描述了该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、前提条件、安装、单节点在线部署、多节点部署、Prefill-Decode (PD) "
"分离、功能验证、精度和性能评估、性能调优以及常见问题解答。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:9
msgid ""
"The `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` model is first supported in `vllm-"
"ascend:v0.17.0rc1`. Use `v0.17.0rc1` or later for this model. The examples "
"below use the version placeholder configured by the documentation build "
"system."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` 模型首次在 `vllm-ascend:v0.17.0rc1` 中得到支持。请使用 `v0.17.0rc1` "
"或更高版本。以下示例使用文档构建系统配置的版本占位符。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:11
msgid "2 Supported Features"
msgstr "2.支持的特性"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:13
msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix, including BF16, W8A8 quantization, chunked"
" prefill, automatic prefix caching, speculative decoding, asynchronous "
"scheduling, tensor parallelism, expert parallelism, data parallelism, PD "
"disaggregation, and ACLGraph support."
msgstr ""
"请参阅[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型的支持特性矩阵，包括"
" BF16、W8A8 量化、分块预填充、自动前缀缓存、推测解码、异步调度、张量并行、专家并行、数据并行、PD 分离和 ACLGraph 支持。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:15
msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get "
"feature configuration details."
msgstr "请参阅[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:18
msgid ""
"The support matrix records the maximum verified capability for this model. "
"The startup examples in this document use practical validation settings for "
"online serving and performance testing. Adjust `--max-model-len`, `--max-"
"num-seqs`, and `--max-num-batched-tokens` based on your service workload and"
" available KV cache."
msgstr ""
"支持矩阵记录了该模型已验证的最大能力。本文档中的启动示例使用实际验证设置进行在线服务和性能测试。根据您的服务工作负载和可用 KV 缓存调整 "
"`--max-model-len`、`--max-num-seqs` 和 `--max-num-batched-tokens`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:21
msgid "3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "3.前提条件"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:23
msgid "3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "3.1 模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:25
msgid ""
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` (BF16 version): requires 2 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) nodes"
" or 4 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes. [Download model "
"weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B)."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B`（BF16 版本）：需要 2 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）节点或 4 个 Atlas 800 "
"A2（64G × "
"8）节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:26
msgid ""
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8` (quantized version): requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x"
" 16) node or 2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes. [Download model "
"weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-"
"Tech/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp)."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8`（量化版本）：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）节点或 2 个 Atlas "
"800 A2（64G × 8）节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-"
"Tech/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:28
msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to a shared directory across "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`, so that all serving nodes can load "
"the same path."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`，以便所有服务节点可以加载相同路径。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:30
msgid "3.2 Verify Multi-node Communication (Optional)"
msgstr "3.2 验证多节点通信（可选）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:32
msgid ""
"If you want to deploy the model in a multi-node environment, verify the "
"communication environment according to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)."
msgstr ""
"如果要部署多节点环境，需要按照[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-"
"communication)验证多节点通信。"

