#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:91
msgid "5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "5.在线服务部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:93
msgid "5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "5.1 单节点在线部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:95
msgid ""
"Single-node deployment runs both Prefill and Decode on the same node. It is "
"suitable for functional validation, long-context single-cluster serving, and"
" W8A8 deployment on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node. The W8A8 version needs "
"`--quantization ascend`."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在同一节点上运行 Prefill 和 Decode。适用于功能验证、长上下文单集群服务以及在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × "
"16）节点上的 W8A8 部署。W8A8 版本需要 `--quantization ascend`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:97
msgid ""
"Run the following script to execute online 128K inference on 1 Atlas 800 A3 "
"(64G x 16)."
msgstr "运行以下脚本在 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上执行 128k 长度的在线推理。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:138
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the service fails to start, HBM is insufficient, or "
"requests are not scheduled as expected, refer to [FAQs](../../faqs.md) "
"first, and then check the model-specific FAQ in Section 10."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果服务启动失败、HBM 不足或请求未按预期调度，请先参阅[常见问题解答](../../faqs.md)，然后检查第 10 节中的模型特定"
" FAQ。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:140
msgid "**Key parameters:**"
msgstr "**关键参数：**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:142
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-size 1` and `--tensor-parallel-size 16` set DP and TP for "
"one 16-NPU A3 node."
msgstr ""
"`--data-parallel-size 1` 和 `--tensor-parallel-size 16` 设置一个 16-NPU A3 节点的 DP"
" 和 TP。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:143
msgid ""
"`--enable-expert-parallel` enables expert parallelism for MoE layers. Do not"
" mix MoE tensor parallelism and expert parallelism in the same MoE layer."
msgstr ""
"`--enable-expert-parallel` 为 MoE 层启用专家并行。不要在同一个 MoE 层中混合使用 MoE 张量并行和专家并行。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:144
msgid ""
"`--max-model-len` is the maximum input plus output length for a single "
"request. Increase it only when enough KV cache is available."
msgstr "`--max-model-len` 是单个请求的最大输入加输出长度。仅在拥有足够 KV 缓存时增加此值。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:145
msgid ""
"`--max-num-seqs` is the maximum number of active requests scheduled by each "
"DP group. For performance tests, set `--max-num-seqs * --data-parallel-size`"
" greater than or equal to the test concurrency."
msgstr ""
"`--max-num-seqs` 是每个 DP 组调度的最大活动请求数。对于性能测试，设置 `--max-num-seqs * --data-"
"parallel-size` 大于或等于测试并发数。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:146
msgid ""
"`--max-num-batched-tokens` is the maximum number of tokens processed in one "
"scheduler step. A larger value can improve prefill efficiency but consumes "
"more activation memory."
msgstr ""
"`--max-num-batched-tokens` 是一个调度步骤中处理的最大 token 数。较大的值可以提高预填充效率，但会消耗更多激活内存。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:147
msgid ""
"`--gpu-memory-utilization` controls how much HBM vLLM can use to calculate "
"KV cache capacity. A higher value increases KV cache size but can trigger "
"OOM if runtime memory is higher than the profile run."
msgstr ""
"`--gpu-memory-utilization` 控制 vLLM 可用于计算 KV 缓存容量的 HBM 量。较高的值会增加 KV "
"缓存大小，但如果运行时内存高于 profile 运行，可能会触发 OOM。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:148
msgid ""
"`--enable-prefix-caching` enables prefix caching. For Qwen3.5, short "
"prefixes may not be cached when the hybrid KV cache manager adjusts the "
"block size to a large value."
msgstr ""
"`--enable-prefix-caching` 启用前缀缓存。对于 Qwen3.5，当混合 KV "
"缓存管理器将块大小调整为较大值时，短前缀可能不会被缓存。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:149
msgid ""
"`--quantization ascend` enables Ascend quantization for the W8A8 model. "
"Remove this option when deploying the BF16 model."
msgstr "`--quantization ascend` 为 W8A8 模型启用 Ascend 量化。部署 BF16 模型时请移除该选项。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:150
msgid ""
"`--speculative-config` enables Qwen3.5 MTP speculative decoding. Reduce "
"`num_speculative_tokens` or remove this option if the workload is sensitive "
"to first-token latency or if MTP is unstable in your environment."
msgstr ""
"`--speculative-config` 启用 Qwen3.5 MTP 推测解码。如果工作负载对首 token 延迟敏感，或者 MTP "
"在您的环境中不稳定，请减少 `num_speculative_tokens` 或移除该选项。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:151
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables "
"full decode ACLGraph replay to reduce dispatch overhead."
msgstr ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 启用完整解码 "
"ACLGraph 重放以减少调度开销。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:152
msgid ""
"`--additional-config` enables Ascend-specific optimizations. "
"`enable_fused_mc2` enables MoE fused operators, `enable_flashcomm1` enables "
"FlashComm1, and `enable_cpu_binding` enables Ascend-native CPU binding."
msgstr ""
"`--additional-config` 启用 Ascend 特定优化。`enable_fused_mc2` 启用 MoE "
"融合算子，`enable_flashcomm1` 启用 FlashComm1，`enable_cpu_binding` 启用 Ascend 原生 CPU"
" 绑定。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:154
msgid "5.2 Multi-Node Deployment with MP (Recommended)"
msgstr "5.2 使用 MP 的多节点部署（推荐）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:156
msgid ""
"Multi-node MP deployment uses vLLM data parallelism across nodes and tensor "
"parallelism within each node. It is recommended for the W8A8 model on 2 "
"Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes."
msgstr ""
"多节点 MP 部署使用 vLLM 跨节点数据并行和每个节点内的张量并行。推荐用于 2 个 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点上的 W8A8 "
"模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:158
msgid ""
"Assume you have 2 Atlas 800 A2 nodes and want to deploy "
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp` across them. Replace `nic_name`, `local_ip`, "
"and `node0_ip` with the actual network interface and IP addresses in your "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"假设您有 2 个 Atlas 800 A2 节点，并希望跨多个节点部署 `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp` 模型。将 "
"`nic_name`、`local_ip` 和 `node0_ip` 替换为您环境中的实际网络接口和 IP 地址。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:160
msgid "Run the following script on node 0."
msgstr "在节点 0 上运行以下脚本。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:206
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If node 1 cannot join the service or HCCL initialization "
"times out, refer to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication) and "
"[FAQs](../../faqs.md). Make sure the network interface names, IP addresses, "
"and RPC ports are consistent across nodes."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果节点1无法加入服务或HCCL初始化超时，请参考[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-"
"multi-node-communication)和[常见问题解答](../../faqs.md)。确保各节点的网络接口名称、IP地址和RPC端口一致。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:208
msgid "Run the following script on node 1."
msgstr "在节点1上运行以下脚本。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:258
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the headless node exits immediately, check whether "
"node 0 is already running, whether `--data-parallel-address` points to node "
"0, and whether `--data-parallel-start-rank` is unique for each node."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果无头节点立即退出，请检查节点0是否已在运行、`--data-parallel-"
"address`是否指向节点0，以及每个节点的`--data-parallel-start-rank`是否唯一。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:260
msgid ""
"If the service starts successfully, the following information is displayed "
"on node 0:"
msgstr "如果服务启动成功，节点0上将显示以下信息："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:271
msgid "**Key parameters for MP deployment:**"
msgstr "**MP部署的关键参数：**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:273
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-size` is the global DP size across all nodes. In the "
"example, 2 DP ranks are used."
msgstr "`--data-parallel-size`是所有节点的全局DP大小。示例中使用了2个DP rank。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:274
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-size-local` is the number of DP ranks on the current node. "
"In the example, each A2 node has 1 local DP rank."
msgstr "`--data-parallel-size-local`是当前节点上的DP rank数量。示例中每个A2节点有1个本地DP rank。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:275
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-start-rank` is the first DP rank on the current node. Node "
"0 starts from 0 by default, and node 1 starts from 1."
msgstr "`--data-parallel-start-rank`是当前节点上的起始DP rank。节点0默认从0开始，节点1从1开始。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:276
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-address` must point to the master DP node. Use node 0 "
"`local_ip` on node 0 and `node0_ip` on other nodes."
msgstr ""
"`--data-parallel-address`必须指向主DP节点。在节点0上使用节点0的`local_ip`，在其他节点上使用`node0_ip`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:277
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-rpc-port` is the DP RPC port. Use the same value on all "
"nodes and ensure the port is available."
msgstr "`--data-parallel-rpc-port`是DP RPC端口。在所有节点上使用相同的值，并确保端口可用。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:278
msgid ""
"`--api-server-count` controls how many API server processes are started on "
"the master node."
msgstr "`--api-server-count`控制主节点上启动的API服务器进程数量。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:279
msgid ""
"`--headless` starts a worker node without exposing an API server. Use it on "
"non-master nodes."
msgstr "`--headless`启动一个不暴露API服务器的工作节点。在非主节点上使用。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:280
msgid ""
"`--tensor-parallel-size 8` maps one TP group to the 8 NPUs on each A2 node."
msgstr "`--tensor-parallel-size 8`将一个TP组映射到每个A2节点上的8个NPU。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:281
msgid ""
"`HCCL_IF_IP`, `GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`, `TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`, and "
"`HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` bind HCCL, Gloo, and TP communication to the selected "
"network."
msgstr ""
"`HCCL_IF_IP`、`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`、`TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`和`HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME`将HCCL、Gloo和TP通信绑定到所选网络。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:282
msgid ""
"`multistream_overlap_shared_expert` overlaps shared expert computation for "
"better throughput on MoE workloads."
msgstr "`multistream_overlap_shared_expert`重叠共享专家计算，以提高MoE工作负载的吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:284
msgid "5.3 Multi-Node Deployment with Ray"
msgstr "5.3 使用Ray的多节点部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:286
msgid ""
"For Ray-based distributed deployment, refer to [Ray Distributed "
"(Qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B)](../features/ray.md). The same model weight, "
"communication verification, and parameter tuning principles apply to "
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B."
msgstr ""
"对于基于Ray的分布式部署，请参考[Ray分布式部署(Qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B)](../features/ray.md)。相同的模型权重、通信验证和参数调优原则适用于Qwen3.5-397B-A17B。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:288
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If Ray workers cannot discover each other, check Ray "
"cluster status first, then verify the same HCCL and network interface "
"settings used in MP deployment."
msgstr "常见问题提示：如果Ray工作节点无法互相发现，请先检查Ray集群状态，然后验证MP部署中使用的相同HCCL和网络接口设置。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:290
msgid "5.4 Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
msgstr "5.4 预填充-解码分离部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:292
msgid ""
"PD disaggregation separates Prefill and Decode into different service "
"groups. Prefill nodes process large prompt chunks, Decode nodes serve token "
"generation, and a proxy forwards requests between them. This mode is "
"suitable for production serving scenarios where prefill and decode resource "
"ratios need to be tuned separately."
msgstr ""
"PD分离将预填充和解码划分为不同的服务组。预填充节点处理大型提示块，解码节点负责token生成，代理在两者之间转发请求。此模式适用于需要分别调整预填充和解码资源比例的生产服务场景。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:294
msgid ""
"We recommend using Mooncake for deployment. Refer to "
"[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) for the "
"general PD disaggregation workflow."
msgstr ""
"我们推荐使用Mooncake进行部署。有关通用PD分离工作流程，请参考[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:296
msgid ""
"Take Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) as an example. We recommend deploying 1P1D with"
" 3 nodes for `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp`:"
msgstr ""
"以Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）为例，我们建议部署1P1D（3节点）来运行`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp`："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:298
msgid "1 Prefill node: 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16)."
msgstr "1个预填充节点：1台Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:299
msgid "2 Decode nodes: 2 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16)."
msgstr "2个解码节点：2台Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:301
msgid ""
"Deploy `run_p.sh`, `run_d0.sh`, and `run_d1.sh` on the corresponding nodes, "
"and deploy a proxy script on the prefill master node to forward requests."
msgstr "在相应节点上部署`run_p.sh`、`run_d0.sh`和`run_d1.sh`，并在预填充主节点上部署代理脚本以转发请求。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:303
msgid "5.4.1 Prefill Node"
msgstr "5.4.1 预填充节点"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:305
msgid "Create `run_p.sh` on the prefill node."
msgstr "在预填充节点上创建`run_p.sh`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:377
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the prefill service is not ready for a long time, "
"check whether the model path is shared, `ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` contains"
" all 16 NPUs, and the Mooncake `kv_port` is available."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果预填充服务长时间未就绪，请检查模型路径是否共享、`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`是否包含全部16个NPU，以及Mooncake的`kv_port`是否可用。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:379
msgid "5.4.2 Decode Node 0"
msgstr "5.4.2 解码节点0"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:381
msgid "Create `run_d0.sh` on the first decode node."
msgstr "在第一个解码节点上创建`run_d0.sh`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:459
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If decode node 0 fails to initialize, check that "
"`MASTER_IP_ADDRESS` points to decode node 0 itself, `--data-parallel-start-"
"rank` is 0, and `kv_connector_extra_config.decode.dp_size` matches the "
"global decode DP size."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果解码节点0初始化失败，请检查`MASTER_IP_ADDRESS`是否指向解码节点0本身、`--data-parallel-"
"start-rank`是否为0，以及`kv_connector_extra_config.decode.dp_size`是否与全局解码DP大小匹配。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:461
msgid "5.4.3 Decode Node 1"
msgstr "5.4.3 解码节点1"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:463
msgid "Create `run_d1.sh` on the second decode node."
msgstr "在第二个解码节点上创建`run_d1.sh`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:541
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If decode node 1 cannot join decode node 0, check that "
"`--headless` is set, `--data-parallel-start-rank` is 8, and `--data-"
"parallel-address` points to decode node 0."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果解码节点1无法加入解码节点0，请检查是否设置了`--headless`、`--data-parallel-start-"
"rank`是否为8，以及`--data-parallel-address`是否指向解码节点0。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:543
msgid "**Key parameters for PD disaggregation:**"
msgstr "**PD分离的关键参数：**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:545
msgid ""
"`--distributed-executor-backend mp` uses multiprocessing on each node for "
"the local workers."
msgstr "`--distributed-executor-backend mp`在每个节点上使用多进程处理本地工作节点。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:546
msgid ""
"Prefill uses `--data-parallel-size 8`, `--data-parallel-size-local 8`, and "
"`--tensor-parallel-size 2`. This creates 8 local DP groups, each with TP2."
msgstr ""
"预填充使用`--data-parallel-size 8`、`--data-parallel-size-local 8`和`--tensor-"
"parallel-size 2`。这将创建8个本地DP组，每个组使用TP2。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:547
msgid ""
"Decode uses `--data-parallel-size 16`, `--data-parallel-size-local 8`, and "
"`--tensor-parallel-size 2`. Decode node 0 starts from DP rank 0 and decode "
"node 1 starts from DP rank 8."
msgstr ""
"解码使用`--data-parallel-size 16`、`--data-parallel-size-local 8`和`--tensor-"
"parallel-size 2`。解码节点0从DP rank 0开始，解码节点1从DP rank 8开始。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:548
msgid ""
"`--data-parallel-address` and `--data-parallel-rpc-port` define the DP "
"control plane. For decode nodes, the address must point to decode node 0."
msgstr ""
"`--data-parallel-address`和`--data-parallel-rpc-"
"port`定义DP控制平面。对于解码节点，地址必须指向解码节点0。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:549
msgid ""
"`--max-num-batched-tokens` is larger on the prefill node and smaller on "
"decode nodes because prefill is prompt-token intensive while decode is "
"latency sensitive."
msgstr ""
"`--max-num-batched-tokens`在预填充节点上较大，在解码节点上较小，因为预填充是提示token密集型，而解码对延迟敏感。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:550
msgid ""
"`recompute_scheduler_enable` sends requests back to the prefill side to "
"recompute KV cache when decode KV cache is insufficient. Enable it on both "
"prefill and decode nodes in PD mode."
msgstr ""
"`recompute_scheduler_enable`在解码KV缓存不足时将请求发送回预填充端重新计算KV缓存。在PD模式下，在预填充和解码节点上都启用它。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:551
msgid ""
"`--kv-transfer-config` sets the Mooncake connector. `kv_role` is "
"`kv_producer` on prefill and `kv_consumer` on decode."
msgstr ""
"`--kv-transfer-"
"config`设置Mooncake连接器。`kv_role`在预填充上为`kv_producer`，在解码上为`kv_consumer`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:552
msgid ""
"`kv_connector_extra_config.prefill.dp_size/tp_size` and "
"`decode.dp_size/tp_size` must match the actual global DP and TP layout."
msgstr ""
"`kv_connector_extra_config.prefill.dp_size/tp_size`和`decode.dp_size/tp_size`必须与实际全局DP和TP布局匹配。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:553
msgid ""
"`--no-enable-prefix-caching` disables prefix caching. For PD disaggregation,"
" the D-node prefix-cache known issue is tracked in "
"[#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/7944)."
msgstr ""
"`--no-enable-prefix-"
"caching`禁用前缀缓存。对于PD分离，D节点前缀缓存的已知问题在[#7944](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/issues/7944)中跟踪。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:554
msgid ""
"`VLLM_MOONCAKE_ABORT_REQUEST_TIMEOUT` is the timeout in seconds for "
"automatically releasing the prefiller KV cache for a request."
msgstr "`VLLM_MOONCAKE_ABORT_REQUEST_TIMEOUT`是自动释放请求的预填充器KV缓存的超时时间（秒）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:555
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\": \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` is "
"recommended on decode nodes to reduce decode dispatch overhead."
msgstr ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\": "
"\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'`建议在解码节点上使用，以减少解码调度开销。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:557
msgid "5.4.4 Request Forwarding"
msgstr "5.4.4 请求转发"

