msgstr ""
"在与预填充服务实例相同的节点上运行代理服务器。您可以在仓库示例中获取代理程序：[load_balance_proxy_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)。"

