#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:678
msgid "9.2 Tuning Guidelines"
msgstr "9.2 调优指南"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:680
msgid ""
"Refer to [public performance tuning "
"documentation](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)"
" for general tuning methods, and refer to [feature "
"matrix](../../user_guide/support_matrix/feature_matrix.md) for feature "
"descriptions."
msgstr ""
"通用调优方法请参考[公开性能调优文档](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)，功能描述请参考[特性矩阵](../../user_guide/support_matrix/feature_matrix.md)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:682
msgid "Recommended tuning order:"
msgstr "推荐调优顺序："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:684
msgid ""
"Set the deployment topology first. Use single-node deployment for "
"validation, MP deployment for simple multi-node serving, and PD "
"disaggregation when prefill and decode need different resource ratios."
msgstr "首先设置部署拓扑。验证阶段使用单节点部署，简单多节点服务使用MP部署，当prefill和decode需要不同资源比例时使用PD分离部署。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:685
msgid ""
"Choose the maximum context length with `--max-model-len`. Long context "
"increases KV cache usage, so reduce `--max-num-seqs` or `--gpu-memory-"
"utilization` if OOM occurs."
msgstr ""
"通过`--max-model-len`选择最大上下文长度。长上下文会增加KV缓存使用量，若发生OOM，请降低`--max-num-"
"seqs`或`--gpu-memory-utilization`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:686
msgid ""
"Tune `--max-num-batched-tokens`. Larger values usually improve prefill "
"throughput but increase activation memory. Decode-heavy workloads usually "
"need smaller values."
msgstr ""
"调优`--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`。较大值通常能提升prefill吞吐量，但会增加激活内存。decode密集型工作负载通常需要较小值。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:687
msgid ""
"Tune `--max-num-seqs` according to service concurrency. Requests above this "
"value wait in the queue and the waiting time is counted in TTFT and TPOT."
msgstr "根据服务并发度调优`--max-num-seqs`。超过此值的请求将在队列中等待，等待时间计入TTFT和TPOT。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:688
msgid ""
"Tune `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Increase it to provide more KV cache, but "
"leave headroom for runtime memory fluctuation and expert imbalance."
msgstr "调优`--gpu-memory-utilization`。增大该值可提供更多KV缓存，但需预留空间应对运行时内存波动和专家负载不均衡。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:689
msgid ""
"Tune `--speculative-config`. MTP can improve decode throughput, but the best"
" `num_speculative_tokens` depends on acceptance rate and workload."
msgstr ""
"调优`--speculative-"
"config`。MTP可提升decode吞吐量，但最佳`num_speculative_tokens`取决于接受率和工作负载。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:690
msgid ""
"Tune ACLGraph capture. `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` is recommended for decode. If you "
"set `cudagraph_capture_sizes` manually, include common decode batch sizes. "
"With FlashComm1, use capture sizes that are multiples of TP size."
msgstr ""
"调优ACLGraph捕获。decode阶段推荐使用`FULL_DECODE_ONLY`。若手动设置`cudagraph_capture_sizes`，需包含常见decode批次大小。使用FlashComm1时，捕获大小应为TP大小的倍数。"

