#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:707
msgid "10 FAQ"
msgstr "10 常见问题"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:709
msgid ""
"For common environment, installation, and general parameter issues, refer to"
" [FAQs](../../faqs.md). This section only covers model-specific issues for "
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B."
msgstr "常见环境、安装和通用参数问题请参考[常见问题](../../faqs.md)。本节仅涵盖Qwen3.5-397B-A17B的模型特定问题。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:711
msgid ""
"Q1: Why does the service report OOM during startup or soon after accepting "
"requests?"
msgstr "Q1：为什么服务在启动时或接受请求后不久报告OOM？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:713
msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** The service fails during profile run, or it starts "
"successfully but reports OOM when real traffic arrives."
msgstr "**现象：** 服务在profile运行期间失败，或成功启动但在真实流量到达时报告OOM。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:715
msgid ""
"**Cause:** Qwen3.5-397B-A17B has high weight and KV cache memory "
"requirements. Large `--max-model-len`, large `--max-num-seqs`, large `--max-"
"num-batched-tokens`, or high `--gpu-memory-utilization` can leave "
"insufficient HBM headroom. Runtime expert load imbalance can also make real "
"inference use more memory than the profile run."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** Qwen3.5-397B-A17B具有较高的权重和KV缓存内存需求。较大的`--max-model-len`、`--max-num-"
"seqs`、`--max-num-batched-tokens`或较高的`--gpu-memory-"
"utilization`可能导致HBM预留空间不足。运行时专家负载不均衡也可能导致实际推理使用的内存超过profile运行。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:717
msgid ""
"**Solution:** Use the W8A8 model with `--quantization ascend` when possible,"
" lower `--max-model-len`, lower `--max-num-seqs`, lower `--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`, or reduce `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Keep "
"`PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF=expandable_segments:True`. For BF16 or larger "
"context, use the required number of A2/A3 nodes."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 尽可能使用W8A8模型并配合`--quantization ascend`，降低`--max-model-len`、`--max-"
"num-seqs`、`--max-num-batched-tokens`或`--gpu-memory-"
"utilization`。保持`PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF=expandable_segments:True`。对于BF16或更大上下文，请使用所需数量的A2/A3节点。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:719
msgid "Q2: Why does multi-node MP deployment hang during initialization?"
msgstr "Q2：为什么多节点MP部署在初始化期间挂起？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:721
msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** One node waits for other ranks, HCCL initialization times "
"out, or the headless node exits."
msgstr "**现象：** 一个节点等待其他rank，HCCL初始化超时，或headless节点退出。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:723
msgid ""
"**Cause:** Network interface names, IP addresses, DP ranks, or RPC ports are"
" inconsistent across nodes."
msgstr "**原因：** 各节点间的网络接口名称、IP地址、DP rank或RPC端口不一致。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:725
msgid ""
"**Solution:** Verify multi-node communication first. Ensure `HCCL_IF_IP`, "
"`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`, `TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`, and `HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` match the"
" selected NIC. Ensure all nodes use the same `--data-parallel-rpc-port`, "
"non-master nodes use `--headless`, and `--data-parallel-start-rank` does not"
" overlap."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** "
"首先验证多节点通信。确保`HCCL_IF_IP`、`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`、`TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`和`HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME`与所选NIC匹配。确保所有节点使用相同的`--data-"
"parallel-rpc-port`，非主节点使用`--headless`，且`--data-parallel-start-rank`不重叠。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:727
msgid "Q3: Why is prefix caching disabled in the PD disaggregation examples?"
msgstr "Q3：为什么PD分离示例中禁用了前缀缓存？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:729
msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** PD disaggregation may show abnormal behavior when prefix "
"caching is enabled on decode nodes."
msgstr "**现象：** 在decode节点上启用前缀缓存时，PD分离可能表现出异常行为。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:731
msgid ""
"**Cause:** The D-node prefix-cache issue is a known limitation tracked in "
"[#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/7944)."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** D节点前缀缓存问题是一个已知限制，跟踪于[#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/issues/7944)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:733
msgid ""
"**Solution:** Use `--no-enable-prefix-caching` for PD disaggregation until "
"the limitation is resolved. For non-PD single-node serving, enable prefix "
"caching only when the workload has repeated prefixes and the cache hit rate "
"is meaningful."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 在该限制解决前，PD分离请使用`--no-enable-prefix-"
"caching`。对于非PD单节点服务，仅当工作负载包含重复前缀且缓存命中率有意义时，才启用前缀缓存。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:735
msgid ""
"Q4: Why does performance regress after enabling FlashComm1 or Fused MC2?"
msgstr "Q4：为什么启用FlashComm1或Fused MC2后性能下降？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:737
msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** Throughput decreases, latency increases, or MoE load becomes"
" unstable after enabling communication or MoE fusion optimizations."
msgstr "**现象：** 启用通信或MoE融合优化后，吞吐量下降、延迟增加或MoE负载变得不稳定。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:739
msgid ""
"**Cause:** These optimizations are workload dependent. FlashComm1 is most "
"useful in high-concurrency TP scenarios. Fused MC2 may not be suitable for "
"some multi-DP large-token cases where padded tokens overload certain "
"experts."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** 这些优化依赖于工作负载。FlashComm1在高并发TP场景中最有效。Fused "
"MC2可能不适用于某些多DP大令牌场景，其中填充令牌会使某些专家过载。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:741
msgid ""
"**Solution:** Compare with `enable_flashcomm1` disabled and "
"`enable_fused_mc2` set to 0. If FlashComm1 is enabled and you tune "
"`cudagraph_capture_sizes`, use values that are multiples of TP size. Keep "
"the better setting for your actual concurrency and prompt length "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** "
"与禁用`enable_flashcomm1`并将`enable_fused_mc2`设为0的情况进行对比。若启用了FlashComm1并调优`cudagraph_capture_sizes`，请使用TP大小的倍数。根据实际并发度和提示长度分布保留更优设置。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:743
msgid "Q5: How should I tune MTP speculative decoding for this model?"
msgstr "Q5：如何针对此模型调优MTP推测解码？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:745
msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** MTP improves throughput in some workloads, but may increase "
"first-token latency or provide limited benefit in others."
msgstr "**现象：**MTP在某些工作负载中可提升吞吐量，但在其他场景下可能增加首token延迟或收益有限。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:747
msgid ""
"**Cause:** The benefit depends on speculative token acceptance rate, request"
" length, and decode concurrency."
msgstr "**原因：**收益取决于推测token接受率、请求长度和解码并发度。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B.md:749
msgid ""
"**Solution:** Start with `num_speculative_tokens` set to 3 as shown in this "
"document. If the service is latency-sensitive or the acceptance rate is low,"
" reduce the value or remove `--speculative-config` and compare TTFT, TPOT, "
"and throughput."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：**按本文档所示，初始将`num_speculative_tokens`设置为3。如果服务对延迟敏感或接受率较低，请减小该值或移除`--speculative-"
"config`，并比较TTFT、TPOT和吞吐量。"

